== 命名 ==
[[雨树属|Samanea]]是雨树的拉丁学名，因为其巨大的伞状树冠被广泛认知，其宽度可以达到20至30米。Samanea公司在其品牌中使用，寓意着该公司矢志成长为一棵擎天大雨树，为中小商户出海遮风挡雨。<ref>{{Cite web|title=An Avenue of Heritage Rain Trees.|url=https://www.nparks.gov.sg/gardens-parks-and-nature/heritage-trees/ht-2015-269|access-date=2022-05-27|work=National Parks Board|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220616032325/https://www.nparks.gov.sg/gardens-parks-and-nature/heritage-trees/ht-2015-269}}</ref>

